                    | \`hello\` | Say hello to someone |

                    ## Related Packages

                    - [sdk-go](https://github.com/${ORG}/sdk-go) — Plugin SDK
                    - [gen-go](https://github.com/${ORG}/gen-go) — Generated Protobuf types
